8
00:00:45,080 --> 00:00:46,640
Hello. I am Wen Xin.

9
00:00:46,920 --> 00:00:47,920
Hello. I am Sun Wen.

10
00:00:47,920 --> 00:00:48,000
Hello. I am Sun Wen.

11
00:00:48,000 --> 00:00:49,060
Hello. I am Sun Wen.

12
00:01:33,960 --> 00:01:36,479
Right. The truck driver.

13
00:01:38,479 --> 00:01:40,360
If, on June 1st,

14
00:01:40,360 --> 00:01:42,880
