19
00:02:05,320 --> 00:02:06,120
Mom.

20
00:02:08,000 --> 00:02:08,800
Okay.

21
00:02:09,199 --> 00:02:12,080
Mrs. Chen, I have something very important to do right now.

22
00:02:12,080 --> 00:02:14,040
Let's talk about this later, okay?

23
00:02:14,040 --> 00:02:16,040
