24
00:02:16,040 --> 00:02:16,900
Let me tell you,

25
00:02:17,000 --> 00:02:19,360
Jianjian earned the money in this house.

26
00:02:19,360 --> 00:02:21,000
Don't even think about taking his assets.

27
00:02:21,000 --> 00:02:22,200
Get out of here now.

28
00:02:23,640 --> 00:02:24,440
Mom.

29
00:02:28,200 --> 00:02:29,000
Mom.

30
00:02:29,280 --> 00:02:31,560
Mom, what are you doing with these?

31
00:02:31,800 --> 00:02:32,520
Move.

32
00:02:32,840 --> 00:02:33,560
Mom.

33
00:02:33,960 --> 00:02:35,640
Is this Chen Jian's home?

34
00:02:38,720 --> 00:02:40,520
Yes. Who are you?

35
00:02:40,520 --> 00:02:42,200
