46
00:03:02,560 --> 00:03:04,760
Let's take this stuff to cover the debt.

47
00:03:05,200 --> 00:03:05,720
Don't touch that.

48
00:03:05,720 --> 00:03:07,050
Don't be unreasonable.

49
00:03:07,240 --> 00:03:08,600
Don't you touch that.

50
00:03:32,920 --> 00:03:37,600
Don't touch anything.

51
00:03:44,079 --> 00:03:46,280
Mom, keep an eye on the house.

52
00:03:46,760 --> 00:03:48,880
Everyone, let's talk this out.

53
00:03:49,000 --> 00:03:50,460
Please don't hurt anyone.

54
00:03:50,600 --> 00:03:52,480
