61
00:04:13,360 --> 00:04:13,840
Wenxin.

62
00:04:13,920 --> 00:04:14,360
Mom.

63
00:04:15,000 --> 00:04:16,120
You bitch.

64
00:04:16,440 --> 00:04:19,040
