65
00:04:19,160 --> 00:04:21,160
How could you be so heartless?

66
00:04:21,200 --> 00:04:23,200
My son won't let you off, even as a ghost.

67
00:04:23,200 --> 00:04:24,720
Mom, enough.

68
00:04:26,720 --> 00:04:29,760
You saw it yourself. Your son owes people a lot of money.

69
00:04:29,760 --> 00:04:31,220
If you cut ties with me now,

70
00:04:31,240 --> 00:04:32,560
