71
00:04:32,560 --> 00:04:34,360
If you keep making a scene, I'm done.

72
00:04:34,360 --> 00:04:35,720
You come here making trouble every other day.

73
00:04:35,720 --> 00:04:37,380
I'll sell the house and leave.

74
00:04:38,000 --> 00:04:40,040
You can deal with the rest yourself.

75
00:04:42,880 --> 00:04:45,080
If you still want me to handle this mess,

76
00:04:46,400 --> 00:04:47,760
