81
00:05:19,080 --> 00:05:19,920
Wenxin.

82
00:05:21,480 --> 00:05:22,280
I'm here.

83
00:05:22,880 --> 00:05:23,680
I'm here.

84
00:05:24,240 --> 00:05:26,360
The accident happened at 4:00 PM on June 1st.

85
00:05:26,360 --> 00:05:27,080
That means,

86
00:05:27,080 --> 00:05:28,240
in the space-time you are in,

87
00:05:28,240 --> 00:05:30,280
