88
00:05:30,280 --> 00:05:30,800
I live in

89
00:05:30,800 --> 00:05:32,640
Room 502, Building 18, Hubin Minyuan.

90
00:05:32,640 --> 00:05:34,960
My husband is Chen Jian, and my daughter is Xixi.

91
00:05:34,960 --> 00:05:35,760
Also,

92
00:05:36,280 --> 00:05:37,600
the truck driver's number.

93
00:05:37,600 --> 00:05:40,640
13830395232.

94
00:05:40,960 --> 00:05:42,280
If he doesn't show up that day,

95
00:05:42,280 --> 00:05:44,000
you can still prevent the accident.

96
00:05:44,000 --> 00:05:45,000
Okay, I got it.

97
00:05:45,360 --> 00:05:48,040
I'll be waiting here for your news every morning.

98
00:05:48,040 --> 00:05:50,370
Please, you must talk to me no matter what.

99
00:05:50,480 --> 00:05:52,140
The lives of my family of three

100
00:05:52,640 --> 00:05:54,000
are in your hands.

101
00:05:57,400 --> 00:05:58,200
Okay.

102
00:05:59,640 --> 00:06:00,440
Leave it to me.

103
00:06:13,520 --> 00:06:14,560
Hubin Minyuan.

104
00:06:15,240 --> 00:06:16,040
Chen Jian.

105
00:06:16,640 --> 00:06:17,840
Xixi.

106
00:06:30,560 --> 00:06:32,040
Hello, Miss Wen. I am Sun Wen.

107
00:06:32,040 --> 00:06:32,680
On the afternoon of June 1st,

108
00:06:32,680 --> 00:06:34,080
