115
00:06:41,440 --> 00:06:43,080
Otherwise, you'll encounter danger on the way.

116
00:06:43,080 --> 00:06:44,720
Then how should I repay you?

117
00:06:48,840 --> 00:06:50,770
If she's not that easy to talk to...

118
00:06:59,440 --> 00:07:00,440
You might not believe me,

119
00:07:00,440 --> 00:07:02,000
but I really came specifically to warn you today.

120
00:07:02,000 --> 00:07:02,600
On the afternoon of June 1st,

121
00:07:02,600 --> 00:07:03,240
you must not take your family

122
00:07:03,240 --> 00:07:03,880
camping in the suburbs.

123
00:07:03,880 --> 00:07:05,280
Otherwise, you'll be in danger.

124
00:07:05,280 --> 00:07:06,680
Why should I believe you?

125
00:07:08,560 --> 00:07:09,080
This revolving lantern

126
00:07:09,080 --> 00:07:10,120
can connect to the spacetime 12 days from now.

127
00:07:10,120 --> 00:07:11,120
Wait until midnight,

128
00:07:11,120 --> 00:07:12,360
and you can talk to yourself from 12 days in the future.

129
00:07:12,360 --> 00:07:14,220
You will tell yourself the truth.

130
00:07:17,040 --> 00:07:17,880
Two plans prepared.

131
00:07:17,880 --> 00:07:18,880
Foolproof.

132
00:07:43,440 --> 00:07:44,900
What happened to his hand?

133
00:07:48,560 --> 00:07:49,520
Then tell him.

134
00:07:50,400 --> 00:07:51,560
Just say I said so.

135
00:09:01,480 --> 00:09:02,810
I think I forgot my keys.

136
00:09:03,400 --> 00:09:06,280
Okay, I'll go back and get them now.

137
00:09:21,320 --> 00:09:23,250
I'll get them for you when I'm back.

138
00:09:25,400 --> 00:09:27,440
Who are you? Why are you at my door?

139
00:09:31,800 --> 00:09:32,760
It's you.

140
00:09:33,560 --> 00:09:34,820
You're Wen Xin, right?

141
00:09:37,160 --> 00:09:38,240
Do you know me?

142
00:09:38,240 --> 00:09:40,520
We've met before. You bought my revolving lantern.

143
00:09:40,520 --> 00:09:43,360
I had a stall there. Do you remember?

144
00:09:44,480 --> 00:09:45,600
I remember now.

145
00:09:45,760 --> 00:09:46,760
Do you need something?

146
00:09:46,760 --> 00:09:49,020
I've been looking for you for a long time.

147
00:09:52,360 --> 00:09:53,360
Sorry about that.

148
00:09:54,120 --> 00:09:55,920
Miss Wen, I'm Sun Wen.

149
00:09:56,400 --> 00:09:58,160
What I'm about to tell you

150
00:09:58,160 --> 00:09:59,360
might sound strange,

151
00:09:59,440 --> 00:10:00,440
