156
00:10:07,640 --> 00:10:09,160
Just listen to me first.

157
00:10:09,480 --> 00:10:10,480
You must not go.

158
00:10:10,480 --> 00:10:11,520
You must not go on June 1st.

159
00:10:11,520 --> 00:10:12,200
Because your family

160
00:10:12,200 --> 00:10:13,400
