167
00:10:33,240 --> 00:10:35,840
They can both connect to the spacetime 12 days later.

168
00:10:35,840 --> 00:10:37,040
Wait until midnight,

169
00:10:37,200 --> 00:10:39,400
and you can talk to your future self from 12 days later.

170
00:10:39,400 --> 00:10:41,260
You will tell yourself the truth.

171
00:10:55,080 --> 00:10:56,280
Now do you believe me?

172
00:11:00,640 --> 00:11:02,240
You sold me mine for 58.

173
00:11:02,800 --> 00:11:05,360
