174
00:11:05,880 --> 00:11:06,760
No, Miss Wen.

175
00:11:06,960 --> 00:11:09,000
I'm really not here to sell anything.

176
00:11:09,000 --> 00:11:11,800
Look, I know business is tough.

177
00:11:12,000 --> 00:11:13,280
But I don't need this thing.

178
00:11:13,280 --> 00:11:14,410
Go ask someone else.

179
00:11:14,520 --> 00:11:15,200
That family.

180
00:11:15,200 --> 00:11:16,040
Maybe they need it.

181
00:11:16,040 --> 00:11:16,840
Thanks.

182
00:11:16,880 --> 00:11:19,040
Miss Wen, I know I'm clumsy with words.

183
00:11:19,040 --> 00:11:19,960
I shouldn't be so abrupt

184
00:11:19,960 --> 00:11:21,680
