185
00:11:21,680 --> 00:11:22,880
But you must believe me.

186
00:11:22,880 --> 00:11:24,560
You must not go on the afternoon of June 1st.

187
00:11:24,560 --> 00:11:27,020
You can't gamble with your daughter's life.

188
00:11:30,560 --> 00:11:32,360
