189
00:11:32,960 --> 00:11:34,080
That's not the point.

190
00:11:34,080 --> 00:11:36,410
The point is, Miss Wen, please believe me.

191
00:11:37,280 --> 00:11:37,940
Otherwise,

192
00:11:38,480 --> 00:11:39,280
on June 1st,

193
00:11:39,880 --> 00:11:42,140
