194
00:11:42,520 --> 00:11:43,480
What did you say?

195
00:11:54,560 --> 00:11:57,090
Do scammers start in acting school nowadays?

196
00:11:57,120 --> 00:11:58,920
Why are you all such good actors?

197
00:12:00,040 --> 00:12:02,120
This isn't how it's supposed to go.

198
00:12:02,520 --> 00:12:04,560
Speak. Who told you my address?

199
00:12:04,720 --> 00:12:05,560
How do you know?

200
00:12:05,560 --> 00:12:06,360
Miss Wen,

201
00:12:07,040 --> 00:12:08,200
please believe me.

202
00:12:08,200 --> 00:12:09,240
Your daughter and husband

203
00:12:09,240 --> 00:12:10,280
are really in mortal danger.

204
00:12:10,280 --> 00:12:11,640
You're the one in danger!

205
00:12:11,640 --> 00:12:13,040
If you just sit back and do nothing,

206
00:12:13,040 --> 00:12:13,800
